text: Bill Dankbaar (7 November 1952 - 4 March 2013) was an Australian rower. He competed in the men's eight event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1952 births Category:2013 deaths Category:Australian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Australia Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Adelaide
